LEAF NODES (makeLeaf) — survive as-is, no absorption
========================================================================
Semantic Action   C++ Type        nodeValue set to
---------------   -----------     ----------------
#intnum           intNode         token text (e.g. "2")
#floatnum         floatnumNode    token text (e.g. "3.5")
#id               idNode          token text (e.g. "myVar")
#type             typeNode        token text (e.g. "float")
#addop            addopNode       token text (e.g. "+")
#multop           multopNode      token text (e.g. "*")
#relop            relopNode       token text (e.g. "==")
#assign           assignNode      token text (e.g. "=")
#sign             signNode        token text (e.g. "-")
#visibility       visibilityNode  token text (e.g. "public")
#void             voidNode        token text
#self             selfNode        token text
#if               ifNode          token text
#while            whileNode       token text
#read             readNode        token text
#write            writeNode       token text
