These are always leaves (isLeaf=true, no children). They survive untouched unless
a subsequent passAlong absorbs them (which only happens to epsilon sentinels).


========================================================================
SUBTREE NODES (makeSubTree) — may survive OR get absorbed by passAlong
========================================================================
These are created by makeSubTree, which pops N children and groups them.
They survive in the tree IF no passAlong action comes after to absorb them.
If a passAlong does follow, the subtree node is ABSORBED (its data/children
are transferred to the passAlong node and the original is deleted).

Semantic Action        C++ Type Created            Absorbed By
---------------        -------------------         -----------
#classdecl             classdeclNode               #class → classNode
#impldef               impldefNode                 #impl → implNode
#funcdef               funcdefNode                 #func → funcNode
#reptprog0             reptprog0Node               #prog → progNode
#reptfuncbody1         reptfuncbody1Node           #funcbody → funcbodyNode
#reptstatblock1        reptstatblock1Node          #statblock → statblockNode
#reptclassdecl4        reptclassdecl4Node          #class → classNode (indirect, via classdecl)
                                                   
#aparams               aparamsNode                 SURVIVES (no passAlong follows)
#expr                  exprNode                    SURVIVES
#expr2                 expr2Node                   SURVIVES
#fparams               fparamsNode                 SURVIVES
#param                 paramNode                   SURVIVES
#funchead              funcheadNode                SURVIVES
#relexpr               relexprNode                 SURVIVES
#funcdeclfam           funcdeclfamNode             SURVIVES
#attributedeclfam      attributedeclfamNode        SURVIVES
#vardecl               vardeclNode                 SURVIVES
#reptvardecl3          reptvardecl3Node            SURVIVES
#reptfparams3          reptfparams3Node            SURVIVES
#reptfparams4          reptfparams4Node            SURVIVES
#reptimpldef3          reptimpldef3Node            SURVIVES
#reptoptclassdecl22    reptoptclassdecl22Node      SURVIVES
#optclassdecl2         optclassdecl2Node           SURVIVES
